note right of UC1
  User searches for movies
  and adds them to watchlist
  with priority and notes
end note

note right of UC7
  User marks movie as watched
  and can optionally rate it
  and write a review
end note

note right of UC12
  System automatically
  detects binge sessions
  when multiple episodes
  are watched in sequence
end note

note right of UC22
  Personalized feed combines
  similar content discovery
  with genre preferences
end note

note right of UC29
  Generated annually on
  January 1st with option
  to share on social media
end note

note right of UC32
  System monitors streaming
  platforms twice daily and
  notifies users of changes
end note

